<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://wsphotofews.excite.com/027/H2/1G/OE/ma23591.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
1.  Get a bind in Thurgadin.  <br>
2.  Hit the bank and unload your unecessary gear.  <br>
3.  Bring plenty of arrows/shuriken if you are the puller.<br>
4.  Bring back packs for loot.<br>
5.  If it is your first time killing Tizmaks, your faction will be fine.  You can walk all over the caves with out invis.<br>
6.  If you have faction issues with these guys, invis up.<br>
7.  Go to the middle cave near the obelisk/manalith thing (as indicated on the map).  <br>
8. The first cave you see on the left will be your set up cave.  There is a rock there that may have 2 spawns.  Kill them and medd there.  <br>
9.  In that cave there are 4 that will spawn on the west wall of the cave.  Do your best to break up their spawn.  Harmony and mezz are your best bet.  You may have enough room to FD pull and peal but it tough do to closeness.<br>
10.  Once those are broken you can pull wanderers from the hall and also from the other caves.  You really do not need to pull from the first cave on the right, but the 2 tizmaks that spawn there can be single pulled with a bow or shuriken assuming that you pull the one on the left first.  For some reason, if you try to pull the one on the right first, they both come.<br>
11.  Keep that 4 spawn in your cave broken up.  Pullers need to check for pops in there constantly.<br>
12. Beware of Yaka Razorhoof.  He is tuff but if you have a full group you can kill him.  He does not have a single spawn point.  He may spawn in your cave.  He spawn and roam the halls.  He may be at the outside entrance.  He is a freak.  And speaking of Yaka....<br>
13.  Loot.  Here are the drops that you can expect.<br>
a.  Velium weapons.  They will be mostly 1hb and 2hb types of weapons.  They will proc velium shards at 25.  Sell at a vendor for a couple plat.  Also good for pets <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
b.  Tizmak legs arms and Tunic.  Good stuff.  Has the velium leather look. Sell at a vendor for a couple plat<br>
c.  Cured Tizmak Surcoat and Gloves.  This is good stuff.  I have seen people that needed this stuff.  So I would recommend need before greed and that if you win it that you sell in EC.<br>
d.  Tizmak meat.  Used for high end quest.  Don't really need.  Not that hard to get.  Does not sell nor is it used in any recipies.  Destroy em as you see em.<br>
e.  Yaka Razorhoof Drops: Stone etched Velium mace and Gauntlets of power.  These are pretty nifty items.  Definately a need before greed Item.  The mace is the common drop and the Gauntlets are the rare.  Only seen one pair drop and I think Bjarki is wearing them <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
14.  Taking breaks to sell.  You will get much Tizmak leather and velium weapons.  Take turns going to sell or go as a group.  If you do FFA, just go until you are full.  Once all are full and no one has room or the strength to carry more, go sell.<br>
15 <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>    BEWARE OF AREA EFFECT SPELLS</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  There is a bug in the caves that will cause creatures to be unseeable and/or stuck in the walls but still able to attack you.  AE spells are a guaranteed way to get them on you.  If you get one of these, hitting you, run or gate to Thurgadin.  If someone is getting hit by these, DO NOT HEAL THEM unless you are ready to run to Thurgadin as well <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     BTW: always a good idea to have SOW on you. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Well, that is run down on the Tizmaks.  If you need a ride to Velious, send me a tell.  There are also plenty of Tizmaks there to kill.  I would like to see lots of people there to kill these things and get exp.  This is good stuff. <p><img src=http://wsphotofews.excite.com/026/Wa/ze/db/kD45531.jpg> <BR> </p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub20.ezboard.com/fbloodsongfrm21.showMessage?topicID=21.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub20.ezboard.com/fbloodsongfrm21.emailToFriend?topicID=20.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub20.ezboard.com/fbloodsongfrm21.threadControl?topicID=20.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub20.ezboard.com/fbloodsongfrm21.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=20.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub20.ezboard.com/fbloodsongfrm21.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=20.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub20.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="bloodsongbloodsong">Bloodsong<option value="bloodsongfrm24">Pictures<option value="bloodsongfrm25">The Tavern<option value="bloodsongfrm15">History<option value="bloodsongfrm23">Biographies<option value="bloodsongfrm9">New Members<option value="bloodsongfrm22">recruitment forum<option value="bloodsongfrm6">Raids<opt